Thought about this one some more and realized the reason it sucks isn't bc it's rape, it's bc it's not a rape fantasy. Let's be real, most of us enjoy rape fantasies that a) happen to rude/stubborn love interest who's just asking to be fucked with, or b) happens to a character who secretly enjoys it and admits they're into it later. But a real rape scenario--one where the love interest is absolutely sweet and innocent, and the rapist is just a bastard, and neither of them are really happy at the end--that sucks. The rape comes out of nowhere and seems offbeat for the MC. It's not even well-written. It starts off as a cute story between a brother and sister, then devolves into something that makes no sense and is offensive to fantasies in general. In short, even if you're into rape fantasies, this one sucks. :(
